{
  "texts": [
    "MNScore = 1 • EMScore + 4 • BERTScore + 1 • Role-F1 6.",
    "By integrating BERTScore and EMScore, MN-Score achieves the highest correlation with human judgment, making it a reliable metric for assessing movie understanding and narration quality.",
    "CRITIC CRITIC (Han et al., 2024) is designed to evaluate the accuracy of character identification in generated ADs.",
    "It employs a co-referencing model to replace ambiguous pronouns (e.g., he and she) in the ADs with official character names from a pre-defined character bank.",
    "The metric then compares the sets of character names in the generated and ground truth ADs, calculating the intersection over union (IoU) to assess accuracy."
  ]
}